SUMMARY:Spring Break Camps for Kids
DESCRIPTION:Now enrolling! Spend Spring Break with the Schulz Museum! Ice skate at Camp Freeze\, explore stop-motion animation with LEGOs\, cook up tasty snacks\, keep busy with STEAM-based activities\, and more! Space is limited; advance registration required.  \n 
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/spring-break-classes-for-kids-4/
CATEGORIES:Calendar of Events
END:VEVENT
