SUMMARY:Blast Off! (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Countdown to a morning of zooming fun and learn about Snoopy’s adventures in space and on land (real and pretend)! Watch a short movie in the Museum Theater\, make Flying Ace paper airplanes\, and a Joe Motocross mask.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/blast-off-grades-1-3-5/
CATEGORIES:Classes & Camps
END:VEVENT
