SUMMARY:Springtime Workshop (Grades K-6)
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the start of spring with Peanuts-inspired crafts and treats! Make Beagle Scout spring chicks\, an Easter Beagle basket\, a Peanuts spring ornament\, and Snoopy candy huggers with Norene Cox\, creator of partypinching.com and author of Sweet Treats for the Holidays. Advance registration required. 
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/springtime-workshop-family-or-drop-off-grades-k-6/
CATEGORIES:Calendar of Events,Classes & Camps
