DESCRIPTION:On the last Monday of the month\, enjoy stories\, crafts\, and activities designed for children ages 1-5 and their caregivers. This month\, explore the Museum’s newest exhibition\, Snoopy’s Family\, bead friendship bracelets\, create your own portable family portrait\, and dance like Snoopy with a fun dance party!
