DESCRIPTION:Now enrolling! Spend Summer Break with the Schulz Museum! Ice skate at Camp Freeze\, work with professional cartoonists\, explore stop-motion animation with LEGOs\, cook up tasty snacks\, keep busy with STEAM-based activities\, and more! Space is limited; advance registration required. 
