SUMMARY:Outdoor Art and Adventure Mini (Grades TK-K)
DESCRIPTION:Get up\, go\, and create! Keep moving all week with outdoor games and art activities. Explore labyrinths and mosaics\, paint with fly swatters and sticks\, and enjoy fun outdoor eco-crafts. Children must be at least 4 years old to register.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/outdoor-art-and-adventure-mini-grades-tk-k-2/
