SUMMARY:Blast Off! (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Blast off into a week of space\, land\, and sea exploration! Learn about constellations and comets\, explore wheels and ramps\, create a nebula in a jar\, launch water rockets\, and learn about Snoopy’s adventures with NASA and motocross.
